DESIGNATION OF COUNTRIES (STANDARDS COUNCIL OF CANADA) ORDER - which
designates those countries which are parties to the North American Free
Trade Agreement as ones where organizations engaged in standards testing
and certification may be accredited by the Standards Council of Canada.
